Package: wateRinfo
Type: Package
Title: Download TimeSeries Data From Waterinfo.be
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Stijn", "Van Hoey", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "stijnvanhoey@gmail.com",
    comment = "http://orcid.org/0000-0001-6413-3185"))
URL: https://github.com/stijnvanhoey/wateRinfo
Description: The wateRinfo package provides an R interface to the data available
    at waterinfo.be, the data portal provided by the Flemish Environmental
    Agency. The package provides R functions to check the available stations for 
    a given variable, check the available variable for a given station and 
    download time series using the database identifiers as well as station 
    names.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
    httr,
    dplyr,
    jsonlite,
    lubridate (>= 1.6.0),
    rlang
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2,
    dplyr,
    covr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
